{"tid":261971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞賊斬加籍找換店東6秒掠140萬重慶大廈外犯案燒車滅迹","createTime":"2017-05-29T01:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T12:39:29.000Z","uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0311a892d69d22e49b52a91e1cea574cc7a5f8","tid":261971,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"狂斬找換店主　<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南亞黨6秒掠140萬　<br />\n重慶大廈外犯案　燒車滅迹</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在本港經營4間找換店的加拿大籍男子，前晚在尖沙嘴重慶大廈的找換店收舖後，攜着載有40萬元現金的背囊偕同菲律賓籍妻子，行至對面iSQUARE商場對開行人路時，遭4名潛伏的蒙面<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南亞賊</span></strong>從後揮刀狂斬搶劫，事主身中5刀命危，賊人掠去事主載有巨款及一隻值逾百萬元名錶的背囊後，跳乘接應私家車逃去，前後歷時6秒。案發後9小時警方在青龍頭尋獲疑遭兇徒燒毀的賊車，在車內撿獲3把懷疑兇刀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170529&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20037269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170529%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20037269&d=6EYkUlC4fZClXY%2B%2FZB2rRXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8f6ac9dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170529%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20037269&h=dd9f9945\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170529&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20037269</a>"},{"pid":"3af6f6e5c7a2bb24bd58f3e09c63b3f9bde64f8b","tid":261971,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 南亞狗"},{"pid":"919318d1515ac28e54ac58fad654368d82176f79","tid":261971,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f68b447ebe9ca634b74d1fd5b0716c85365e6e","tid":261971,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:11:46.000Z","msg":"我識好多..."},{"pid":"8fadd7506b4db4b383e876718bbff37adff